com.github.springtestdbunit.dataset

Class ReplacementDataSetLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.springtestdbunit.dataset.ReplacementDataSetLoader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataSetLoader

    public class ReplacementDataSetLoader
extends Object
implements DataSetLoader
    A data set loader that uses a ReplacementDataSet to replace specific objects or sub-strings. By default will replace "[null]" with null.
    Author:
    Stijn Van Bael, Phillip Webb
